ps know which side to fight from.</span><hr size=1> One of the hardest things about crowd control is also to make sure that the tanks and blaster as well as healers are all on the same side of the mob, opposite of you.  In some cramped spaces it's a bit harder to established, but they should do their best to not stand next to or behind someone trying to effectively backstab.<br>
<br>
